Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:35.08,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「花映难波津 隆冬且暂隐」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:43.88,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:43.88,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「初春又将至 再绽此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:53.27,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:53.27,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「初春又将至 再绽此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:21:01.11,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かくとだに　えやはいぶきの　さしもぐさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:21:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「情凝意暗结 未及教伊识」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二字决定牌的「情凝」 读第一个字时他就伸出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.62,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(520,658)}かく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说 一字决定牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有「骤雨」「波泛」「久别」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:11.95,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,658)}む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:11.95,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,658)}す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:11.95,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(820,658)}め
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「枯风」「群寂」「静夜」「激流」这七张
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.91,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,658)}ふ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.91,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,658)}さ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.91,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,658)}ほ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.91,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(820,658)}せ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过名人在采访时是这样回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「对我来说 有28张」
